  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK331">
<l>nillā tavaṟṟai nilaiyiṉa veṉṟuṇarum</l>
<l>pullaṟi vāṇmai kaṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>That ignorance which considers those things to be stable which are not so, is dishonourable (to the wise).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
